author: Derek Scally
title: Sweden resists mandatory coronavirus measures
description: Scandinavian state registers more than 2,500 cases by Wednesday and 42 fatalities
content:
While its Nordic neighbours have closed all schools and shops to fight the spread of coronavirus, Swedens latest decree in the crisis has been to impose table service-only in restaurants.
